title: 699. 32 Rookies to Watch + Reaction to Aaron Rodgers Returning to Green Bay
itunes:title: 699. 32 Rookies to Watch + Reaction to Aaron Rodgers Returning to Green Bay
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. On this special show, the guys react to the news of Green Bay Packers quarterback Aaron Rodgers returning to the team and showing up for training camp. Next, the duo give a list of 32 rookies to watch out for, as they discuss one per team.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
